sub_title: BSc International Business Administration at RSM Erasmus University Rotterdam
summary:
I thrive in collaborative environments and enjoy taking on new challenges that allow me to apply my skills and make a contribution that matters!
Throughout my work experience, I have enhanced my skills in team and project management, content creation, advertising, data analysis, and strategizing. I am highly motivated and responsible, with a proven track record of taking initiative and delivering results. 

In addition to my professional experience, my academic journey has provided me with a strong foundation in time management, research, and adaptability. I have also gained valuable experience through volunteering and extracurricular activities, which have allowed me to develop a range of skills and expand my horizons further. That took me to discovering (digital) marketing as a field of the most interest for myself. 

Aside from that, I enjoy creating digital content such as graphics and drawings. You can see the link to my portfolio attached on the profile!
